 Boy: What are the two things?
A family of mice were surprised by a big cat. Father Mouse jumped and and said, “Bow-wow!” The cat ran away. “What was that, Father?” asked Baby Mouse.
punchline: “Well, son, that’s why it’s important to learn a second language.”

setup: My friend said he knew a man with a wooden leg named Smith.
punchline: So I asked him “What was the name of his other leg?”
